{"tid":699349,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【友共情不變】這些回憶 既屬於他倆 也屬於我們","createTime":"2018-06-12T12:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T12:35:12.000Z","uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8056e415ff0e2661457aecdc5e724c4c8ea3ad5e","tid":699349,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194438_57a28e101c4a4e464721bb799bc748f7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194438_57a28e101c4a4e464721bb799bc748f7.gif&h=981fd313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十四年前，我同你第一次見面。兩個唔熟嘅小朋友，象徵式輕輕拍一拍手。又有邊個估到，五年後嘅呢支球隊，會由我地兩條三唔識七𡃁仔一齊撐起？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194439_6d6253a25e044f63dfe7dc83504b0ef2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194439_6d6253a25e044f63dfe7dc83504b0ef2.gif&h=ab2b5625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為熱身賽同聯賽盃主力，見到身前企咗高貝利大帝同黑色大肉腸嘅我地，從來都唔敢諗可以極速上位。但機會係留俾有能力嘅人，火速提升嘅，除咗係我地嘅上陣次數同球技，仲有我地嘅感情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194440_8893918f189ae1fa4de7466309bef15d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194440_8893918f189ae1fa4de7466309bef15d.gif&h=a538fc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾經，我地兩個陌生人只係輕輕拍下手，今日，我地成為戰友，互相拖住對方行。我地開始相信，自己唔只係阿仙奴嘅未來，仲開始係兵工廠嘅現在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194446_6bfc8f6f67d419d537885418f56259e1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194446_6bfc8f6f67d419d537885418f56259e1.gif&h=5586b4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好快好快，我地已經係隊內最受球迷歡迎嘅兩位男主角。你係隊長，我係副隊，你一個眼神我已經知你會點交，我一個手勢你已經知我會點跑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194442_2739eb9378ab879957992aac6021cad7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194442_2739eb9378ab879957992aac6021cad7.gif&h=cd30c6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仔大仔世界，大家都有毛有翼曉飛，你想回家，我想捧盃，為咗有更好嘅前程，兩位隊長不惜背上二五仔之名，離開一手湊大自己嘅爺爺。一齊玩咗七年，始終都要分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194443_fd6fb18ffe28d183e6f281c87a7e02be.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194443_fd6fb18ffe28d183e6f281c87a7e02be.gif&h=7351b0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界好細，球壇更加細。兜兜轉轉，我地終於喺自己嘅成名國重逢。無奈嘅係，你係獅子，我係魔鬼。感情或許猶在，但我地唔再係黃金拍檔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194444_a29a637ae54c1fe0cee61479c23fe6a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194444_a29a637ae54c1fe0cee61479c23fe6a7.gif&h=5d4afbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從來都冇諗過，我地仲有機會一齊作戰。今日再見面，大家都成長咗唔少，有唔同嘅經歷。不經不覺，我同你都已經係個準備退休嘅阿叔，但呢十幾年共同作戰嘅回憶，我地一世都會記得。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/203255_de17bfab5a22920b72a317b744966339.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F203255_de17bfab5a22920b72a317b744966339.gif&h=5a44ffbd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}